{"tid":2300200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旺角中心女醫染疫過去數日照常診症","createTime":"2020-11-25T10:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T11:30:05.000Z","uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"31560735cd60454fb1712996f63a60cc162e75f7","tid":2300200,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】消息指，本港新增約86宗新冠病毒確診個案，旺角中心一名婦產科醫生證實感染新冠病毒。<br />\n<br />\n感染新冠病毒的是婦產科專科醫生劉黃色鳳，她於旺角中心一期十八樓仲堅醫療中心應診，診所暫停營業消毒清潔。<br />\n<br />\n診所職員表示，按照衞生防護中心建議於本月21至24日到訪診所的病人，要接受病毒檢測。當局稍後會將樣本瓶分派到診所，病人如有需要可到診所領取。<br />\n<br />\n診所職員：「（已經證實醫生確診？）是的。（病人）但不是緊密接觸者風險不是很高，但要做檢測。（衞生署會否聯絡病人？）他們說不會，但可以安排派發樣本瓶，如果你們（病人）需要的話，但可能需時，不會那麼快。」"},{"pid":"d7b989714984de6eb510f99e3c9342cc7bc8f4ea","tid":2300200,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/bomb_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459b11fc8c1f6081ba6a2c9b33b7ce66fdc39599","tid":2300200,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:20:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4892120217a17d913a8368a62dd0fdbd448c053","tid":2300200,"uid":52276,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:21:02.000Z","msg":"個個BB都中招，有大有細九龍新界冇得避"},{"pid":"3e072573f5989c3fd34d02e12d4770d6306a7c29","tid":2300200,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:21:14.000Z","msg":"婦科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51aee664b7edafccd1442f872e782b812c20c543","tid":2300200,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"黃色鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk